item.title: CVE-2014-0104|2024-08-06T09:05:38.996Z -- fence-agents -- fence-agents
item.description: In fence-agents before 4.0.17 does not verify remote SSL certificates in the fence_cisco_ucs.py script which can potentially allow for man-in-the-middle attackers to spoof SSL servers via arbitrary SSL certificates.
